Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隆一 让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再过不久 你和我的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在光亮之下一定有黑影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而处在光亮下的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不会想去做防范
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄金的黎明将要接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500, 1000)}第四夜 黄金的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 你的背后好像有些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！这不是血吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳子！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道路魔？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这段时间内就有十三件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被害者都是因为失血休克死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地点大多是在人多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来也有人喜欢花哨的道路魔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目击者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是有目击者的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不会特地来拜托紫藤你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讲得对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是这个伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个伤口是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是夜灵干的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监察部长！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松永小姐 NOS的验尸行动已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回到馆内进行搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去抓夜灵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总部已经行动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太希望有外人加入搜查行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是在协助我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在这里做拜祭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想让总部丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有这种习惯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下把验尸报告交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 应该是由我们来协助你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己中意的女人带着一个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然会不高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱讲 我才不会那么没品味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只专一种味道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中意一种有危险的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为最近夜灵越来越猖狂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以总部才会开始行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越难做了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 一个接着一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在我还不明白界的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一日你会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄金的黎明的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄金的黎明？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有那个义务要看守着它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄金的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果被父母给揭穿…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保 一起去喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我要去一个地方 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保最近都不理人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的 因为她有男朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说在做通勤女友的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得你好像是侦探社的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我叫山崎理保
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你搬家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 因为我双亲住在世田谷区
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关系隆一先生的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道应该怎么讲…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…请你振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为隆一现在在我的身体里面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩就要出生了 是隆一的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷先生和惠小姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我记得泷先生他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他非常有精神 最近常常踢我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是姐姐的手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你快点长大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈也会努力的吸取更多的营养
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…没事 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大冢惠怀孕了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠小姐说是泷先生的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个不是泷 是夜灵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太好 如果她肚子里的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是拥有夜灵血液的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且母体也非常危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近所发生的连续事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个百孔事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不会是惠做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是没有可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果惠小姐肚子里的婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是人类而是夜灵的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们会怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要杀了他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠小姐她非常的相信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是她和泷先生的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何惠小姐每次都要受这种苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄金的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界所讲的黄金的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是指这件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是这件事 紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:10:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类和夜灵之间的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是这新时代开始的序幕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来带你走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是在和人类纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再继续下去了 如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果以我们吸血鬼为主的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类就像是朵云一样 过眼云烟罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我消失！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是冷酷的寒暄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对特别来看你的恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我比你活得还要久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是打不赢我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 下次我还会再来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 告诉你一个消息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大冢惠被NOS抓起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讲什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想把大冢惠怎么处理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他们给拉开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手！这是命令！快放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫、紫藤…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咕哩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 这是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的孩子做了什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我！放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手！别碰她！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:13:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊！不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个家伙也是夜灵 把他抓起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让他逃脱了 快追！快追！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住！ 可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生真慢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松永弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么时候认识那个男人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道那个男人紫藤龙彦是个吸血鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有没有性行为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有被吸过血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤是个可以相信的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然又对人类… 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止到底是为了什么而躲避着界的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不必烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类本来就只能算是我们的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.23,0:15:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀不了惠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然连她肚子里的孩子也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会来临的黄金的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经有觉悟和我一起走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想从夜灵手中保护人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类和夜灵的小孩并不是现在才有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你一直固执自己是个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才会不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有想过为什么吸血鬼会有永远的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为拿人类来做交换
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是神想让我们成为历史的旁观者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以给我们的特权
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你看守着黄金的黎明 你就会明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对历史一点兴趣都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤 你跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在悠久的时光流逝的那段时期
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们生活在德莱堡的那种日子正等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德莱堡…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦人的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤快想想那时在德莱堡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再做吸血鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不知道为何我们会永生的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就给你一个例子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要乱动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！停手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要杀就杀我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为与紫藤扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会有这种下场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再过数分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会因为失血过多而死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:17:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！我要杀死你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？想杀死给你永远生命的我？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再讲了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界！别一直利用幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现真身出来和我打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你在哪里了 界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是杀不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤那家伙到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保！振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在去叫医生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保！振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有用的 紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:19:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比你多活数百年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我的力量会比你大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再问你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿不愿意跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿不愿意与我一起守着黄金黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西跟我一点关系都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个愚蠢的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把嘴放干浄一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我纵坏你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我必须要重头管教你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可、可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是我对你的一种爱 紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤…你真的要杀死我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为吸血鬼前的过去都将会永远消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回忆一下 紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在德莱堡的那些日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们互相相爱的那段时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界…我很喜欢现在这种生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以过去的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.08,0:21:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来讲已经不重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.91,0:21:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咕哩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.72,0:21:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保！振作一点！理保！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.27,0:21:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话 她一定会死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.30,0:22:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.48,0:22:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你吸我的血…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.91,0:22:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！你想像我一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.67,0:22:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能见光不能死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能在夜晚行动的冰冷身体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.28,0:22:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不想和紫藤先生分开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.91,0:22:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想永远和你在一起 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.81,0:22:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.05,0:22:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.21,0:22:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.19,0:23:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个可爱的婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隆一 跟姐姐打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.79,0:23:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再见了 隆一
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.91,0:23:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果那个连续杀人事件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.03,0:23:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是惠小姐干的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.31,0:23:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 她那种笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够诞生新生命的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.32,0:23:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会做那种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.10,0:23:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生 那是你的幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.59,0:23:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古语有云
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.16,0:23:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲是最坚强的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.04,0:23:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 女人最可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.52,0:24:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比夜灵更加可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.13,0:24:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.09,0:24:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我后悔把你的时间给停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.26,0:24:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想永远的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.70,0:24:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一日你一定会恨我的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.04,0:24:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恨我让你得到永远的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.43,0:24:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.20,0:24:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你是这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.79,0:24:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.76,0:24:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不需要同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.19,0:24:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直是这样想着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.14,0:24:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不知为何我却多出这些同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.29,0:24:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保 弥生在等着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.42,0:24:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.47,0:26:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天来临
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.73,0:26:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透明的风吹过
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.36,0:26:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你却消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.82,0:26:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银幕的那边
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.52,0:26:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Night Walker 第五夜
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.95,0:26:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死者的药
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.55,0:26:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不想要…什么永远
